OL,3,CBelfast Trust Board chair sacked as
OL,4,C'fresh start is required'
OL,6,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt has asked
OL,7,Fthe Belfast Trust Board chair, Ciaran
OL,8,FMulgrew to step down as a "change of
OL,9,Fleadership" is needed.
OL,11,FThe Belfast Trust has been under the
OL,12,Fhighest level of intervention since
OL,13,FUTV exposed the findings of a report
OL,14,Finto bullying and poor behavior within
OL,15,Fthe Royal Victoria Hospital's cardiac
OL,16,Fsurgery unit.
OL,18,FSince then whistleblowers have come
OL,19,Fforward and raised concerns about
OL,20,Fother parts of the Belfast Trust.
