OL,3,CBelfast Trust Board chair sacked as
OL,4,C'fresh start is required'
OL,6,FThere have been a series of crisis'
OL,7,Fwithin the trust including the delayed
OL,8,Fmaternity hospital and the fallout
OL,9,Ffrom several high profile inquiries.
OL,11,FThat is even before Mr Mulgrew took up
OL,12,Fhis post around two years ago, however
OL,13,Fthe trust's handling of recent issues
OL,14,Fappear to have prompted the minister
OL,15,Fto act.
OL,17,FUTV will approach Ciaran Mulgrew for
OL,18,Fcomment.
