OL,3,CBelfast Trust Board chair sacked as
OL,4,C'fresh start is required'
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Department of
OL,7,FHealth said: "Health Minister Mike
OL,8,FNesbitt has decided on a change of
OL,9,Fleadership at Belfast HSC Trust.
OL,11,F"The current Trust chair will cease to
OL,12,Fhold the post from Friday 4th July.
OL,14,F"The Minister believes a fresh start
OL,15,Fis required for the Trust.", they
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,F"The Minister and Department would
OL,19,Flike to publicly thank Mr Mulgrew for
OL,20,Fhis contribution to the Trust and the
OL,21,Fwider Health and Social Care system.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
