OL,6,F"A process for filling the chair's
OL,7,Fpost is being initiated as a priority."
OL,9,FDUP member of the Assembly's Health
OL,10,FCommittee Diane Dodds said the
OL,11,Fdevelopment reflected the "sheer scale
OL,12,Fof crisis" within the trust.
OL,14,FBut she highlighted that many of the
OL,15,Fissues pre-dated Mr Mulgrew's tenure.
OL,17,F"Responsibilities within the trust go
OL,18,Fmuch wider than simply one individual
OL,19,Fand the Department of Health will have
OL,20,Fhad an awareness of these issues
OL,21,Falso," she said.
