OL,6,F"The Health Estates division in the
OL,7,Fdepartment has an army of professional
OL,8,Fadvisers who have worked hands in
OL,9,Fglove with the Belfast trust on its
OL,10,Fmajor capital projects and decision-
OL,11,Fmaking around them. Removing the chair
OL,12,Fof the Belfast trust will not deflect
OL,13,Fscrutiny away from many of the
OL,14,Fminister's senior officials.
OL,16,F"There is a wider systemic problem
OL,17,Fwithin the Belfast trust that will not
OL,18,Fbe resolved by simply removing one
OL,19,Findividual.
