OL,6,F"However, we will need to hear more
OL,7,Fdetail about what exactly has prompted
OL,8,Fthis decision at this time. That is
OL,9,Fsomething I will continue to probe
OL,10,Fboth within the Health Committee and
OL,11,Fbeyond."
OL,13,FThe interim chief executive of the
OL,14,FBelfast trust, Maureen Edwards,
OL,15,Fthanked Mr Mulgrew for his "unwavering
OL,16,Fsupport, contribution and commitment".
OL,18,F"Since his appointment, Ciaran has
OL,19,Fhelped us through some very
OL,20,Fchallenging times," she said.
