OL,6,F"In particular, he has shown courage
OL,7,Fand leadership over the last few
OL,8,Fmonths in bringing focus and
OL,9,Fcommitting to addressing issues around
OL,10,Fculture and behaviours in our
OL,11,Forganisation. Ciaran always
OL,12,Facknowledges the fantastic work of
OL,13,Fstaff in Belfast trust and is proud of
OL,14,Ftheir many achievements.
OL,16,F"He is leaving the organisation with
OL,17,Four gratitude and best wishes for the
OL,18,Ffuture.
